data.description: Do you want new construction but also need to be moved in by the Holidays? How about a nice backyard too? Welcome to 6232 S Bell Street! Built in 2019, the first floor features beautiful LVP floors, an open concept design, tons of natural light, waterfall quartz island & a slider off the family room to a private back yard & trex-deck perfect for all your BBQs. Upstairs is a convenient laundry room, 3 guest bedrooms with a tiled bath & a huge primary suite complete with 2 walk-in closets. Close to Wapato Park, I-5 & JBLM, this home is move in ready & will be stress free for years to come. Don’t miss the attached garage, Leaf Guard gutters & fruit bushes in the backyard. VA Assumable loan with a mortgage rate at 3%.
